        <span class="section-tag">Warning Signs</span>
        <h2>Signs You Might Be Deficient: Beyond Obvious Joint Pain</h2>

        <p>Both deficiencies present with a wide range of symptoms that extend well beyond the joints. Many patients are surprised to learn that what they assumed were unrelated complaints — fatigue, pins and needles, low mood — are all part of the same nutritional picture.</p>

        <h3>Vitamin D3 Deficiency Symptoms</h3>
        <div class="symptom-grid">
          <div class="symptom-item">
            <div class="symptom-icon si-red">⬇</div>
