          </div>
          <div class="symptom-item">
            <div class="symptom-icon si-red">⬇</div>
            <div class="symptom-text">Frequent infections due to impaired immune function</div>
          </div>
          <div class="symptom-item">
            <div class="symptom-icon si-red">⬇</div>
            <div class="symptom-text">Depression, mood changes, or cognitive fog</div>
          </div>
          <div class="symptom-item">
