        <div class="warning-box">
          <div class="warning-icon">⚡</div>
          <p><strong>Critical Warning:</strong> B12 deficiency causes neurological damage that is <strong>irreversible if left untreated for too long</strong>. Peripheral neuropathy, once established, may only partially recover even with aggressive supplementation. Early detection is not optional — it is urgent.</p>
